ormal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1097b5cae1ffc75b5febbae7bdcecfa3764b7b04","tid":632351,"uid":3842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8a542a9f93fa8cb6f3d0c2744ce7e69f9957959","tid":632351,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T17:50:18.000Z","msg":"想知盲人發夢會唔會見到顏色？<br />\n因為夢係腦所產生 唔係眼<br />\n佢地發夢會唔會有境像？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T18:09:12.000Z","msg":"如果係天生盲 夢只會得其餘四感 <br />\n如果係後天盲 因為有見過顏色 圖像等等 發夢係可以夢到影像"},{"pid":"dd21e8babf4c21df752d0e4f5e136dc78564205d","tid":632351,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82b1784cf249bd8c225d2943fcf7250f3d5e341f","tid":632351,"uid":2419,"like":272,"dislike":5,"score":267,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T10:11:28.000Z","msg":"咪冇囉 概咩念<br />\n甚至唔知黑色係黑色 要人特登講先知"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T18:10:25.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"c6d8234ddf1e15c5a7e03db9ac13f7b1f4ec464b","tid":632351,"uid":233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T18:14:39.000Z","msg":"現時科技有冇可能可以令盲人睇得返野？"},{"pid":"3404c3c7e681272f479b796fbf47df5d81e52b83","tid":632351,"uid":162892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T18:15:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果後天盲人<br />\n佢以前見過唔同嘅顏色 係而家盲咗<br />\n咁佢哋發夢會點呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨係見到類似以前見過嘅嘢?<br />\n如果有好多新野佢可能摸過但係冇睇過 佢發夢又會唔會見到呢 or even會係咩色呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n問題好似好白癡 但係我諗極都諗唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n識視障朋友<br />\n如果係後天失明，發夢有時係有色彩的"},{"pid":"9980bb97c7c1747eb9195b4cab45280cad2beb1a","tid":632351,"uid":162892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T18:19:46.000Z","msg":"老師會用一啲物品嘅特徵去表達顏色<br />\n正如樓上有巴打講太陽/ 血就等於紅色，代表織熱或血腥，會用唔同嘅感官讓視障朋友認識呢個世界"},{"pid":"d8fbebfc4287df6b54